 		+ 15% Spell Range<br><br>Extended Enhancement 	+ 15% Spell Duration 	Beneficial Spells Only<br>						Not Complete Healing <br>						Not Invulnerability Spells<br><br><br>Reagent Conservation 	-15% Chance of Reagent Use <br><br><br>Improved Damage 	+ 20% Spell Damage 	No DoTs, AEs, Banes<br><br><br>Enhancement Haste 	+ 30% Spell Haste 	Beneficial Spells Only<br>						Min Cast Time: 3 sec<br>                                                Min Duration: 72 sec<br><br><br>Mana Preservation 	- 10% Spell Mana Cost 	Not Complete Healing<br><br><br>Spell Haste 		+ 15% Spell Haste 	Not Complete Healing<br>						Min Cast Time: 3 sec<br><br><br>Affliction Haste 	+ 33% Spell Haste 	Damaging Spells Only<br>						Min Cast Time: 3 sec<br>						Min Duration: 36 sec<br><br><br>Extended Affliction 	+ 20% Spell Duration	Damaging Spells Only<br>						Min Duration: 36 sec<br><br><br>Affliction Efficiency 	- 25% Mana Cost 	Damaging Spells Only<br>						Min Duration: 36 sec<br><br><br>Summoning Haste 	+ 30% Spell Haste 	Summoned Pets Only<br><br><br>Reanimation Haste 	+ 30% Spell Haste 	Summon Skeleton Pets Only<br><br><br>Summoning Efficiency	- 25% Spell Mana Cost 	Summoned Pets Only<br><br><br>Reanimation Efficiency 	- 25% Spell Mana Cost	Summon Skeleton Pets Only <br></pre><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umissfoxfyre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miss Foxfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/5/02 2:48:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=93.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://gwynhyfar.homestead.com/files/hm9.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Focus Items</span><hr size=1> Please feel free to reformat the last part or all of it.